{"tid":1532291,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「重要」聽日點? 聽日點？繼續罷！","createTime":"2019-09-02T13:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T15:09:42.000Z","uid":129867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1132d19d0a868ff0df97d48db634248e8bb8eddf","tid":1532291,"uid":129867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:14:25.000Z","msg":"據我所知，聽日一樣會有學生繼續罷課<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q</span>：點解開左學更加要罷？<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">A</span>：因為依家更加唔可以俾政府同班狗批中，因為暑假先咁多人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">A</span>：因為我地呢場仗打左3個月，如果因為開學一個咁細既壓力我地就放棄，咁你地之前連條命都唔理個種憤怒去左邊？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今日有份罷既，唔該KEEP住度火</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今日照常返學而感到內疚既，唔該勇敢啲再次企返出黎</span><br />\n<br />\n但真心今日902唔滿意，罷課既人唔夠，罷工既少之有少<br />\n唔通香港人打輸仗都冇所謂？"},{"pid":"9669c3226b626ea5e63fc4f0e342e0e654c3b4b3","tid":1532291,"uid":129867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:14:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9248773e62aeb4fd3e793f56232576aeca03516","tid":1532291,"uid":315924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:15:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫推到江永祥仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n仲有幾個鐘就返學啦好緊張<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529552\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529552</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"42dd97166dd559c70069d581082dc3a2d4cf95d2","tid":1532291,"uid":129867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:16:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58f59ad5b3f150ecb3b5d8b17f937616a1a02022","tid":1532291,"uid":129867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:17:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"604c5d0d5ec99e1fa0cb7e171e3387e60cc09584","tid":1532291,"uid":129867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20